## 5️⃣ Rendering Forms in Templates

```html
<!-- Option 1 — as_p: wraps fields in <p> tags (quickest) -->
<form method="post">
    {% csrf_token %}
    {{ form.as_p }}
    <button type="submit">Save</button>
</form>

<!-- Option 2 — as_table: wraps fields in <tr> tags -->
<form method="post">
    {% csrf_token %}
    <table>{{ form.as_table }}</table>
    <button type="submit">Save</button>
</form>

<!-- Option 3 — manual rendering (most control, used in real projects) -->
<form method="post">
    {% csrf_token %}

    <div>
        {{ form.title.label_tag }}   <!-- <label>Title:</label> -->
        {{ form.title }}             <!-- <input type="text">   -->
        {{ form.title.errors }}      <!-- validation errors     -->
    </div>

    <div>
        {{ form.content.label_tag }}
        {{ form.content }}
        {{ form.content.errors }}
    </div>

    <button type="submit">Save</button>
</form>
```

